# Secrets for the Cloudflare lane (`wrangler dev` / the Deploy to Cloudflare
# button prompt from this file). Slack credentials are NOT listed here on
# purpose: the /admin Slack-connection wizard collects and stores them after
# deploy, once the worker URL exists.

# Admin token gating every /admin route (page + API). The app returns 404 for
# /admin until this is set. Generate one with: openssl rand -hex 32
TAG_ADMIN_TOKEN="replace-with-a-random-hex-string"

# Optional: unlock the Anthropic catalog provider for a smarter default model.
# Without it, the seeded profiles run keyless on the Workers AI binding
# (@cf/zai-org/glm-5.2). Deliberately NOT an active line: the Deploy to
# Cloudflare button renders every key in this file as a REQUIRED prompt
# (verified live 2026-07-07), and this one must stay optional. Set it after
# deploy instead:
#   npx wrangler secret put ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
